# Processed artifacts (data/processed/, data/processed_oos_*/) are committed
# intentionally, alongside data/raw/, so that estimation-artifact drift is
# visible via `git diff` instead of silently going stale relative to
# FINDINGS.md's reported numbers. Re-run scripts/run_estimation.py and commit
# the result whenever model code changes.

# Exception: raw FEC bulk "all committee transactions" files are multi-GB
# and exceed GitHub's 100MB per-file limit. Keep these local-only; they can
# be re-fetched via scripts/fetch_data.py.
